title: Interpreting s(3)
text: Because the input to the s-function is time, $$t=3$$ represents 3 minutes, and s(3) is the number of sit-ups completed in 3 minutes.

title: Putting it together
text: Using s(3) as the input to the function c(s) gives us the number of calories burned during the number of sit-ups that can be completed in 3 minutes.
